# Voice/video TURN relay (optional). Without it, calls are STUN-only and may fail
# between peers on different networks. Get credentials from a TURN provider
# (e.g. metered.ca, Twilio) or self-host coturn. NEXT_PUBLIC_TURN_URL accepts a
# comma-separated list (e.g. "turn:host:3478,turns:host:5349").
